le issue</li>\n<li>Fixed Optimized images</li>\n<li>Fixed Image license</li>\n<li>Fixed Mansory effect for testimonials</li>\n<li>Fixed Mansory effect issue</li>\n<li>Fixed Masonry effect testimonials issue</li>\n<li>Fixed BBpress style</li>\n<li>Fixed Notice The called constructor method for WP_Widget is deprecated since version 4.3.0</li>\n<li>Zerif Lite Welcome page</li>\n<li>Fixed green button label in customizer</li>\n<li>accessibility modification</li>\n<li>accessility modification (remove code in footer.php)</li>\n<li>accessility modification : add alternative text for image in backoffice</li>\n<li>accessility modification : checkbox to enable accessibility. Used to not open some links in a new tab</li>\n<li>accessility modification : add some translated sentances + adapt keyboard navigation for child link in menu</li>\n<li>Fixed Accesibility ready tag</li>\n<li>Fixed moved widgets inside corresponding sections in customizer for easier use</li>\n<li>Removed unused files and optimized images for child themes</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.3 - 24/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update style.css</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.2 - 24/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed upload image button in widgets</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with reCaptcha</li>\n<li>Fixed added bootstrap glyphicons</li>\n<li>Fixed translations for contact form placeholders and added default po and mo file, plus translations for romanian</li>\n<li>Update class-tgm-plugin-activation to latest version</li>\n<li>Fixed placeholders for contact form in IE9</li>\n<li>Update .pot file</li>\n<li>Fixed RTL issue</li>\n<li>Fixed #162 Home latest news responsive issue AND unclosed elements issue</li>\n<li>Removed glyphicon</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.2 - 01/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed allow widgets in our team widget, position field</li>\n<li>Fixed show first image in post if no featured image is selected for latest posts section ; fixed number of latest news section posts</li>\n<li>Fixed added Create a