(259, 1, '2017-01-17 08:42:38', '2017-01-17 08:42:38', '<h1>Achievements and Awards</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Diamond Challenge:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWinner of The Diamond Challenge Tunisia Grand Prize and International honorable mention at the University of Delaware ( business venture track )\r\n<blockquote><em>The Diamond Challenge</em> is a venture concept competition for high school students and young entrepreneurs focused on building business or social ventures. - Diamond Challenge Official Website</blockquote>\r\nThe project:\r\n\r\nTomorrow School ( Summer Academy ) cares deeply about improving computer science education, and sparking passion in students to build real products, combining practical and theoretical education. The goal of this project is to inevitably lessen unemployment in Tunisia , the Arab Nations ,and the World .\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-328" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/DC_Logo_Standard-300x63.png" alt="" width="300" height="63" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tomorrow''s leaders scholarship:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>The Tomorrow’s Leaders Scholarship Program is a U.S.-Middle East Partnership Initiative (MEPI) program for\r\ncapable and highly motivated high school seniors in the Middle East and North Africa who are from underserved backgrounds. The program will provide four-year and 5-year university scholarships (dep\r\nending on the major) and internship opportunities at select institutions of higher learning in the Middle East to students who have the potential to become leaders.  The primary objective of MEPI''s Tomorrow''s Leaders scholarship program is to build a cadre of university-age leaders who are ci<img class="wp-image-327 alignleft" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Seal_of_the_United_States_Department_of_State.svg_-300x300.png" alt="" width="178" height="178" />vic-minded, intellectually able, and professionally skilled, who will become the community, business, and national leaders of the future.\r\n\r\n-Amideast Website</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>National Sea-rowing Championship Bronze medal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Skills</h2>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Technical</h4>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Skills & Achievements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'achievements-and-awards', '', '', '2017-01-17 15:05:10', '2017-01-17 15:05:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/?page_id=259', 0, 'page', '', 0),
